carcycle_price_service.owls.description: This service returns purchase prices of the pair of a car and cycle (the prices contain both new or used cars or cycles).

carbicycle_price_service.owls.description: This service returns purchase prices of the pair of a car and bicycle (the prices contain both new or used cars or bicycles).

4wheeledcarbicycle_price_service.owls.description: This service returns purchase price of the pair of a four wheeled car and bicycle.

bicycleauto_price_service.owls.description: This service returns latest purchase market price of the requested pair of an auto model and a bicycle model.

autobicycle_price_service.owls.description: This service returns daily renting price of the pair of an auto model and a bicycle model.

auto2personbicycle_price_service.owls.description: This service returns daily renting price of the pair of an auto model and 2(two) person bicycle.

bicyclecar_price_service.owls.description: This service returns daily renting price of the requested pair of a car model and a bicycle model.

1personbicyclecar_price_TheBestservice.o.description: It is the best service that returns renting price of the given pair of a car model and 1(one) person bicycle model. The price of car and bicycle pair is for one day rent.

1personbicyclecar_price_service.owls.description: This service returns renting price of the pair of a car model and one person bicycle model. The price of car and bicycle is for one day rent.

autocycle_price_service.owls.description: This service returns weekly renting price of the given pair of an auto model and a cycle model.
